fields.value: Discovery of genomic variants associated with genebank historical traits for rice improvement: SNP and indel data, phenotypic data, and GWAS results

publicationCitation.value:
Pre-publication, to be updated on acceptance:

Sanciangco MD, Alexandrov NN, Chebotarov D, King RD, Naredo MEB, Leung H,
Mansueto L, Mauleon RP, Orhobor OI, McNally KL (2018) Discovery of genomic variants associated with genebank historical traits for rice improvement. submitted.

fields.value: Plink files are compressed bed/bim/fam files containing SNPs and indels derived from the 3000 rice genome datasets (see http://snp-seek.irri.org/_download.zul for "3K RG 4.8mio filtered SNP Dataset" and "3K RG 2.3mio biallelic indel Dataset"). EMMAX files (csv) contain SNP/indel IDs, chromosome and location, uncorrected and corrected p-values. Manhattan and Q-Q plots are images (png).  Manhattan plots can be viewed interactively at http://snp-seek.irri.org/_gwas.zul. Users can also view SNP annotations when selecting regions containing <5000 SNPs at GWAS peaks.
